parser

Class VideoData

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.VideoData

  • public class VideoData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates a new VideoData object. It contains the source file path of the video file, and the (x,y) position of the top-left corner of the video frame.
    Version:
    2.1
    Author:
